put some oil in the pan,

00:06:35.780 --> 00:06:39.965
put it over medium heat,
saute for eight to 10 minutes

00:06:39.965 --> 00:06:42.870
the onions until they're
soft and translucent.

00:06:42.870 --> 00:06:46.810
I like to remind people that we
want to look for visual cues,

00:06:46.810 --> 00:06:47.310
