So you could certainly do one
thing with a piece at a time.

00:36:38.422 --> 00:36:40.380
But if you stack them
over each other like that

00:36:40.380 --> 00:36:43.900
and overlap them a little
bit, you'll go faster.

00:36:43.900 --> 00:36:45.570
So that's just a
really pretty way

00:36:45.570 --> 00:36:48.219
to make something look a little
bit nicer for your salad.

