And so I like to
cut something off

00:37:08.940 --> 00:37:11.620
like a sweet potato,
a potato, carrots,

00:37:11.620 --> 00:37:15.190
I always like to give myself a
steady base when I'm slicing.

00:37:15.190 --> 00:37:17.674
So then I'm just going
to cut right through.

